HOWTO compile the modules:

- Ensure the KERNELDIR in the Makefile in this dir points to this kernel
- Type the following on the command line.

# make ARCH=i386 CROSS_COMPILE=

- You will get virtcan.ko. Insert the kernel module

# insmod virtcan.ko

- Access the virtual CAN drivers at
  /dev/can1 (major=91, minor=0) through /dev/can7 (major=91, minor=6)
